Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.00,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Town Along the River (continued)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.71,0:00:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It still hasn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is this what you're looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...Rei Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rei Kiriyama\NMATCH NOTIFICATION
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.01,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHUB
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the time has come\Nto play against each other in a public forum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:20.14,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CREAK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This came to my house,\Nso I figured you would get one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I came over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I just felt like I had to deliver\Nthis letter to you with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.78,0:00:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you opened my mailbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without permission, Nikaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've waited for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.96,0:00:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, it took me two years longer to reach\N4th dan, but now is the real beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The beginning of true battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You even opened the envelope!\NThat's a crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:00:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think, ever since the day\NI first played against you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at the National Children's Shogi Championship\Nten years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I decided you'd be my lifelong rival and\Never since, I put in effort to progress every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.19,0:01:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I researched under the moonlight,\Nread books by the light of fireflies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and told myself\Nthat I was just a late bloomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, in the end, I too am a genius...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, see you at the game. Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen when somebody's talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.00,0:01:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take it, right from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This declaration of war\Nin the form of a game notification!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just call the federation myself for the info.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me off like that, Kiriyama!\NWe're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? This is the first I'm hearing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it usually goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're rivals, we put in effort,\Nand after overcoming those things,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the end! We'll!\NHigh five each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:54.11,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FRIENDSHIP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:54.11,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EFFORT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:54.11,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BFFs
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go with the flow here!\NThis is the standard for boys' manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The main character\Nof an orthodox boys' manga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't open somebody else's mail and\Nappear with a smug expression on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where's Mr. Hanaoka?\NHe's usually with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you for always taking\Ngood care of Young Master.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In appreciation of his 45 years of service\Nto the Nikaido family,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we gifted him an 80-day cruise\Naround the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}BA-BAAM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BA-BAAM! Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master Harunobu,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please take special care of your health\Nuntil I return.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,80 days? Then this strange beast\Nwill be loose the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, about our upcoming game,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if I go first, will you go\Nwith a One-Turn Loss Bishop Exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or a Cornering Rook?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you go first,\Nwill you do an Attacking Central Rook?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell you, but how would you know\Nif I was telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. Don't be so cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, once we start,\Nyour strategy will be obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then why not keep your eyes peeled\Non that day and confirm it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.73,0:03:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's different.\NI'm just trying to mentally prepare myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to help you\Nwith your mental preparation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, these cakes are delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's not even listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MIKAZUKI-DOU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.57,0:03:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Mr. Hanaoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:28.00,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Town Along the River
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I like the river.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There aren't many things that I like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but when I see a lot of water\Ngathered together,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I go into a daze as my mind becomes quiet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only one subway stop to Sendagaya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but on match days,\NI like to look at the river on the way,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I walk to the nearest JR Station.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I cross various bridges as I go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's strangely soothing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}maybe because when I was young, I lived\Nin a town surrounded by a river on all sides.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although my memories\Nof that time are faint now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A pro shogi player\Nhas 30 to 40 matches per year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there are title matches other than\Nrank-deciding competitions,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}most of them in tournaments,\Nso the more you win,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the more matches you'll play.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:06:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are some top-class players\Nwho have 70 to 80 matches a year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today's match is the qualifier for the NHK Cup.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I make it past the qualifying round\Nof this TV station-sponsored tournament,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and participate in the final tournament,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then, you can guess from the name,\N"NHK Cup"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it'll be broadcast nationwide.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me win this match and be on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May I beat my opponent, Kiriyama,\Nwith my way of shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,May I incinerate his amoeba, conventional\Nbook play with my burning manly soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kyaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you run?\NDid you just try to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know what that is?\NThat's called a "spiritual defeat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His name is Issa Matsumoto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rank C-2, 26 years old, 5th dan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His playing style is aggressive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In fact, all he does is attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He charges at his opponent\Nlike a wild boar or a ball of fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I can't see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What? S-Scary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Knock it off, Issa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}TAHAAAA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh sorry, Smith!\NI can't help but get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}SPIN\NSPIN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}TWITCH\NTWITCH
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I envy how you wear your heart\Non your sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still, cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll scare me so much\Nthat all the pieces in my head could scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Smith.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:07:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rank B-2, 6th dan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:02.56,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180 cm\NKendo Club\N(almost never attends)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:02.56,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,181 cm\NVolleyball Club\N(never attends)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems they get along well\Nbecause they're both tall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well? How's that, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}PAWN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're putting it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}PAWN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}BISHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I take it, his horse will retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}DRAGON HORSE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DRAGON KING
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kiriyama 6 - f - Dragon Horse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Matsumoto 5 - g - Pawn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kiriyama 5 - e - Knight
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Matsumoto 4 - h - Gold General - Retreat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kiriyama 6 - g - Knight - Promoted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Matsumoto 5 - h - Lance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kiriyama 5 - i - Silver General
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not over! It's not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not over, over, not, not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gold General
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}GLOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted his grandpa\Nin the countryside to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His grandpa isn't doing well,\Nso he's in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If NHK broadcasts it,\Nyou can watch from anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Issa was a kid, his grandpa is the one\Nwho taught him how to play shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, cheer up, Issa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Kiriyama said he'll treat us!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna see Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:38.30,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Parallel Displacement\N(5cm per second)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to treat you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, it's fine. Besides, what's the use\Nof a kid having all that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still a minor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't drink liquor, they've got juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fruit, too. Although it's expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Issa is gloomy,\Nthe Shogi Hall gets gloomy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:11:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Matsumoto and Mr. Smith.\NAnd Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akari! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there! You're as beautiful as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Please, have a seat.\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's a totally different person here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...than she is at home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe it really is a different person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Orange juice for you, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for wrapping the sweets\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry. She is the same person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Women are amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I feel much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drinking a lot tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama! You better get your wallet ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky to be in the company of these\Nfun upperclassmen today, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They won't force you to drink,\Nso it's a fun and bright kind of drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I would never\Nforce anyone to drink alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But they're sponging off me against my will.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know this is Ginza, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are scary upperclassmen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The type that would force you\Nto drink until you black out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then abandon you in front of the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?\NWhere are the people you were with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did they leave you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, have some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rokugatsu block.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's near my neighborhood.\NI live in Sangatsu block.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, you're just skin and bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you probably weigh less than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I woke up the next morning,\NI was in that living room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}GONG\NGONG\NWHIRL\NWHIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, he woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want some miso soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was my first time there,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but for some reason,\Nthat old house made me feel nostalgic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was my first time\Nmeeting the three sisters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akari, Hina, and Momo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These would be the kind of people\Nto go out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go out with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.71,0:14:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're kind and reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, you can depend on me for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bullying younger classmen,\Nsponging off of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...is something I would never, ever do!\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, drink up, Kiriyama!\NIt's my treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, well said. That's the Issa I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I the one treating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A toast to Issa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Akari is different from the Akari at home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I think both of them are very beautiful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akari
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:48.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond the Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}The Usual Margarine
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No bread, no instant noodles,\Nno milk, no water.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have toilet paper either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. Guess I'll go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are only warehouses, companies,\Nand factories in Rokugatsu block.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only way I can get food\Nand daily essentials is by crossing{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}this bridge and going\Nto the supermarket on the other side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish there was a bento shop nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like going by myself\Nto diners and street stalls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sangatsu block\Nis on the other side of the bridge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's where Akari and her sisters live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hot... There's no shade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm gonna melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some time after moving to this town,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}no matter where I walked,\Nit felt like I was in a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't hear sounds very well,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the town seemed to flicker\Nin black and white.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:16:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, later on I realized\Nthat I'd been stressed out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About living alone,\Nand in a town I wasn't used to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the moment I met people,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it felt like the other side of the bridge\Nlit up in full color.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They told me to "come over anytime,"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but did they mean it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, just having a place\Nwhere I was told to "come over"...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The words alone made me happy,\Nand my stomach felt full.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That alone felt enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I smell smoke, like something's burning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fireworks?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Super Market - Maru S
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.92,0:16:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's cool in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Obon Festival Preparation Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Obon
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Obon Supplies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's Obon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Instant noodles and sweet buns, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I invite you over to eat,\Nbut you haven't been coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Kiriyama prefers cup noodles\Nover the food Hina and I cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of shocked, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best making the rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I... U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a limit of three to a customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Super Sale - Somen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what we wanted to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We consume a lot of cold noodles\Nin the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And, this is what we're having tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, do you like fried chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then come over. Let's eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.15,0:18:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason, I can't say no to Akari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to vomit. You'll feel better after.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't know how to throw up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all right. Don't bite my finger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. You did good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She saw exactly how pathetic I was\Nfrom the start,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I couldn't keep up any appearance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Do you still have hemp twigs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I sure do. Are you just starting?\NThe sun's about to set.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Shopping took a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- It's later than I thought.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, can you get the baking pan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- The matches, too.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Don't touch it, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, that's right. This was the smell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}It was all throughout the town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Horsies?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:20:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Mom and Grandma\Nrode that to get back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you might not understand yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this is what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My grandma and my mom, all the way\Ndown the line, all did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it you? Are you giving us food today?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up! And a little more than usual, please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your parents buried, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In Nagano.\NThat's my dad's hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job frying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hina did the frying this time.\N- I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The oil spattered me right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. Well, we did fry it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good. Rub some ointment on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's some in one of my drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no reminiscing\Nor anything during dinner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wounds are probably still too fresh,\Nnot even dry, and they're here in this house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was it like for me that time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When did I stop crying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.33,0:21:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How long did it take me\Nto regain my composure?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's strange. I can't remember.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been in a daze for a while...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been in a daze ever since that one day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't find anything else to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing else...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I left, Akari put the leftover rice and\Nchicken into containers, and gave them to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to put them in the fridge\Nwhen you get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Heat them in the microwave\Nwhen you eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come over again on Monday,\Nafter your match is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's the last day of Obon,\Nso I'll make plenty of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Having company over...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"...will be a good distraction."\NThat's what I thought I heard Akari say.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.18,0:22:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but her voice was so soft,\NI couldn't hear her clearly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the way home,\Nthe wind was strong on the bridge,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.82,0:22:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the leftovers I held against my stomach\Nwas warm, like a small animal.{\i0}
