Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:36.51,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.01,0:24:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your rival is waiting for you\Nwith incredible spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.51,0:24:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Kiriyama!\NI got tired of waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.31,0:24:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, is the air conditioning working?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.94,0:24:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.65,0:24:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's heaven compared to the roof\Nof that department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.15,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The last piece of fried chicken...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.45,0:24:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't miss the next episode of\N"March Comes in Like a Lion!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.16,0:24:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to it.
